==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Equivocator
<hw>E*quiv"o*ca`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
equivocates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Here's an <qex>equivocator</qex> that could swear in both the
scales against either scale, yet could not equivocate to heaven.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Equivocatory</ent>⟦br⟧
